Class AccessorPermission

java.lang.Object
com.emc.documentum.rest.model.AbstractLinkable
com.emc.documentum.rest.model.AccessorPermission
All Implemented Interfaces:
Linkable
public class AccessorPermission extends AbstractLinkable
AccessorPermission identify users and groups and define their object-level permissions to the object with which the ACL is associated.
